Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:04.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used\Nas a hint for reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through\Nthe most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, the Detective Boys\Ntake the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The key that unlocks the mystery\Nis a child's drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:15.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again, it's\Nterrible, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Speak for\Nyourself, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man's worth is not\Nin the quality of his art!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But people who are good at drawing are cool\Nand I've got lots of respect for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe tomorrow,\NI'll start going to art classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jukichi Sakai (55)\NSecretary to the President of\NTsubakuro Financial Group
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it smells\Nlike a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:02:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of money, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could that... be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you have\Nall that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please, let me go!\NYoung master is... Young master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Kenzo Tsubakuro"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, my intuition\Nwas right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A kidnapping case\Nhad occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The one who was kidnapped\Nwas Akio Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-kun{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kenzo Tsubakuro (70)\NPresident\NTsubakuro Financial Group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the 5-year-old grandson of Kenzo Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10},\Nthe president of the Tsubakuro Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:27.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akio Tsubakuro (5)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He loves drawing pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:33.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And all those bills were the ransom to get Akio{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-kun{\r\be10} back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, would you care\Nto explain to us in detail what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're pictures Akio drew\Nthat the kidnapper sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you receive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About noon yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were tossed into the mail\Nalong with the threatening letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that is the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"¥1,000,000,000 for the child.\N—The Clown."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! I wonder how many boxed\Neel lunches I could eat for that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the money from before was nowhere near a billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That money was intended to check whether there\Nwas any intention of actually paying the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure at the time the kidnapper was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you lot!\NWe're grateful for your tip,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but from here on in,\Nthis is police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up\Nand go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Inspector, you lot\Nshould go home with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio is my precious and only grandson, who my late son and his wife left me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they passed on in a car crash last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If something were to happen to him,\NI would disgrace his parents in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,\Nbut, Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment we hand over the ransom money\Nto make contact with the culprit kidnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is our perfect shot\Nat arresting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A billion yen is quite a load,\Nso the kidnapper—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me\Nwhether or not you catch the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will not risk Akio's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I am not handing\Nover the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you\Nmean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was in the mailbox\Nthis morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Location for bank transfer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:58.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"locAtIoN foR bAnk TraNsfEr:\NfonTaUbeRt bAnk, SwiTzeRland\Naccount number: 259H604329\Nim COunTinG on You!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fontaubert Bank, Switzerland...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A bank in Switzerland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we should hurry up\Nand place a chargeback,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or at least get the bank to tell us\Nwho the account holder is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Switzerland is a bank nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Swiss banks were so accomodating,\Ntheir existence would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's just as the boy says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthere are no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if doing so\Nbrings Akio back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am asking you...\NLeave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A perfect crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you gave up\Non the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't butt our way into\Npaying the ransom money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,any further than what\NTsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police can't just stand by idly\Nand let this dastardly crime go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So once the ransom money is handed over,\Nand Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} comes back safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're gonna start seriously\Ninvestigating this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But even if the ransom {\i1}is{\i0} paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there's still no guarantee Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} will come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} sure loves to draw, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, can I take another look\Nat Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought,\Nit's here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a quirk of Akio's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he draws something, he puts down\Nwhatever catches his eye as a signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever catches his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I've seen\Nsomething just like that somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really? W-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was at Beika South Kindergarten\Nwhere Akio goes to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they showed me\None of his drawings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika South Kindergarten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Beika South Elementary"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a look at\NAkio Tsubakuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drawing Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s\Ngrandfather saw
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is probably this one\Nhanging here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, teacher.\NWhere did Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} draw this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That signature is the same\Nas what Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} drew here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:39.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Furthermore, what was sent was what\Nhe drew where he was being held hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}if I can figure out where that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can make a good guess\Nas to where Akio{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you up to now, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go on ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're planning to rescue Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nall by yourself, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing\Nwith a kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever danger\Nmight be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this drawing!\NAkio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looks like he's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's smiling as he's watching\NTV with the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's Kamen Yaiba, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I can see from this,\Nhe doesn't seem to be in any sort of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna save him,\Nit's now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you were thinking,\Nwasn't it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, aren't we the ones\Nwho found this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only until we find\Nwhere he's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, we leave it\Nto the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's this that he drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a chimney,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like on a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. Definitely an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he be able\Nto see an alien from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can't see any\Nchimneys from here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you say that,\Nyou're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time for arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chimney or building,\Nit doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look for the thing\Nthat looks like this signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! That's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like a water tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It kinda looks like it\Nand it kinda doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. What do you see\Nin front of that water tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a clock, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a park?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything like\Na park in his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in the middle of the signature\Nthat looks like an eyeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put the clock on top of the water tower,\Nwhat do you think it'd look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. The thing in the signature that\Nlooked like an eye was that clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s in\Nthe water tower, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant. Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s is where it\Nlooks like the clock's in front of the water tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the\Nwater tower, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can see\Nwhere Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you see over there is\Nthe park with the clock from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The eyeball in Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s signature lines up in\Nthe middle of the water tower exactly as he drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it might be a little distorted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} should be being held\Nsomewhere in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh. There's sure a lot\Nof houses around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it doesn't look like\Nwe can really tell from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we split up and search,\Nwe should find him in no time flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you see any suspicious\Npeople or houses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,contact me right away\Non your badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even try to\Ngive chase alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and don't think about\Ngoing to save Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a bunch of\Nsuspicious places, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of them looked like\Nthey could be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still too many places\Nto narrow it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nwhere's Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to meet up\Nat the park at 5:00, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Ayumi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}?!\NWhere are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'d be hungry, so\NI went shopping at a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, what are we gonna\Ndo with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.20,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's way past when we were\Nsupposed to meet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll head back right away,\Njust wait a—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A clown mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? What was that?\NI don't copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10},\Nis something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter,\NAyumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I found a suspicious person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not sure yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but the clown that Akio drew
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.86,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}wore a triangular hat with\Na star on it, had green hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:01.24,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and held a remote\Nin his left hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, it's just like Ayumi said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:10.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means that the kidnapper is left-handed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, don't do anything foolish!\NListen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.38,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found him, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}... He's got to be\Nthe one who kidnapped Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! Stop, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer us, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:37.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:41.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I don't want the kidnapper finding me out,\Nso wait for me to contact you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:41.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She cut us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:50.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! That Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are we going to wait here\Nfor Ayumi to get in touch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be on us if\Nsomething happens to Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you use those glasses of yours\Nto find out where Ayumi is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now the Doc's got them\Nso he can fix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, nothing's gonna happen\Njust staying here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan here!\NAre you there, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tohto Coating Industrial Co., Ltd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back, little boy!\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought you\Nsome sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some crayons\Nand drawing paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were out shopping, Mr. Clown,\NI did a lot of drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you? Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! It's all right,\Nwe're here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?\NHow did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up against us,\Nthe Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give yourself up quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get over here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, there he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Big Sis.\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What a relief!\NReally, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like our strategy\Nwas a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another huge victory\Nfor the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:46.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Afterwards, Inspector Megure and the\Nother police took our information,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}rushed to the scene,\Nand arrested the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But as for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:58.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As we feared, we ended up getting\Na piece of Inspector Megure's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thank you, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out again\Nsometime, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said "Thank you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure feels nice when\Npeople are grateful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:21.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, Akio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} draws really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running ahead\Nof us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez!\NWhy does this always happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A robber!\NSomeone catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went into the alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police!\NFurther escape is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:15.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:\NMPD Detectives' Love Story 4\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Next Conan's Hint: Sunglasses
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:21.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:23.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to Detective\NTakagi and Detective Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It ain't gonna go good,\Nthat's for sure.
